OL,3,CHear from the candidates for Tees
OL,4,CValley Mayor
OL,6,FConservative Ben Houchen has been the
OL,7,Fmayor since 2017, and is hoping for a
OL,8,Fthird term.
OL,10,FHe was made a member of the House of
OL,11,FLords last year.
OL,13,FHe says North Tees Hospital is
OL,14,F"falling down" and he plans to build a
OL,15,Freplacement, as well as providing free
OL,16,Fswimming for children under 11, and
OL,17,Fintroducing more flights from Teesside
OL,18,FAirport "to places like Malaga and
OL,19,FTenerife."
