OL,3,CHear from the candidates for Tees
OL,4,CValley Mayor
OL,6,FLabour candidate Cllr Chris McEwan is
OL,7,Fthe deputy leader of Darlington
OL,8,FBorough Council, and a former NHS
OL,9,Fmanager.
OL,11,FHe said his priorities were growing
OL,12,Fthe economy, "turbo-charging the
OL,13,Fskills system", creating "an
OL,14,Fintegrated transport system", and
OL,15,Fproviding free parking in town centres.
OL,17,FCllr McEwan told us he would be able
OL,18,Fto put the Tees Valley on the map, due
OL,19,Fto his "regional connections and
OL,20,Fnational connections."
