OL,3,CHear from the candidates for Tees
OL,4,CValley Mayor
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrat candidate is
OL,7,FSimon Thorley, who runs a language
OL,8,Ftraining business.JHe is pledging to
OL,9,Fintroduce a #25m annual "early years
OL,10,Fsupport fund" to help those in poverty
OL,11,Fand at risk of poverty, as well as
OL,12,Fmaking local bus services "more
OL,13,Freliable and accessible."JMr Thorley
OL,14,Fclaimed his "concrete, coherent
OL,15,Fpolicies" distinguish him from the
OL,16,Fother candidates.JThe election takes
OL,17,Fplace on Thursday 2 May, with the
OL,18,Fresult expected the following day.
